name: Diana Cazadora
description:
In spirit of Mexican day of Independence (Sept.16th), I am participating in the collective celebration of Mexican NFT artists on this platform. 
The Huntress Diana Fountain is an iconic fountain/statue in the middle of Mexico City, she represents a Roman Goddess, and it thought as 'The Archer of the North Star'. 
She is also a feminist figure, and an inspiration.
The photograph was taken by my and manipulated with slit scan edit style.
